			<table border="0" cellpadding="12" cellspacing="0" width="100%">
				<TR>
					<td valign="top">
<SCRIPT LANGUAGE="JavaScript" SRC="js/DataValidation.js"></SCRIPT><B CLASS="HeadlineText">The Gifts of the Elves</B><BR><BR><FONT size=2><FONT face=Garamond><STRONG><SPAN class=headers>Xanthe`s Earring/PoTC - The Gifts of the Elves</SPAN> </STRONG></FONT></FONT>
<P>
<P><FONT face=Garamond size=2><I>The first three gifts come to us from elven lands. Original writeup courtesy of Xanthe Ravenwolf. Known trivials are now included.</I></FONT></P>
<P><FONT face=Garamond size=2><STRONG>First Gift of the Elves</STRONG></FONT></P>
<P><A href="http://www.eqtraders.com/items/show_item.php?item=1650&amp;menustr="><FONT face=Garamond color=#000000 size=1>Demi-sec Champagne</FONT></A><FONT face=Garamond size=1> </FONT></P>
<UL>
<LI><FONT face=Garamond size=1>Demi Sec Champage = 1 Champagne Magnum + 1 Soda Water + 1 Wine Yeast + 2 Grapes (unstacked) (brew barrel, <I>brewing trivial &gt;250)</I> </FONT></LI></UL>
<P><FONT size=1><FONT face=Garamond><I>Other combines that you need:</I> </FONT></FONT></P>
<UL>
<LI><FONT face=Garamond size=1>Champagne Magnum = 1 Enchanted Gold Bar + 1 Opal+ 1 Bottle (jewelers kit, <I>jewelcraft trivial 195 or 196</I>) </FONT>
<LI><FONT face=Garamond size=1>Soda Water = 1 Soda+ 1 water (brew barrel,<I> brewing trivial 58</I>) </FONT></LI></UL>
<P>
<H4><FONT face=Garamond size=2>Second Gift of the Elves</FONT></H4>
<P><A href="http://www.eqtraders.com/items/show_item.php?item=1621&amp;menustr="><FONT face=Garamond color=#000000 size=1>Mistletoe Cutting Sickle</FONT></A><FONT face=Garamond size=1> </FONT></P>
<UL>
<LI><FONT face=Garamond size=1>Mistletoe Cutting Sickle= Blessed Sickle Blade + Blessed Sickle Hilt + Blessed Sickle Pommel + Smithy Hammer (forge, <I>smithing trivial &gt;250</I>) </FONT></LI></UL>
<P><FONT size=1><FONT face=Garamond><I>Other Combines that you need:</I> </FONT></FONT></P>
<UL>
<LI><FONT face=Garamond size=1>Blessed Sickle Blade = Sheet Metal + Smithy Hammer + Emerald + Curved Blade Mold + Celestial Essence + Blessed Dust of Tunare + Mistletoe Temper (forge, <I>smithing trivial 183</I>) </FONT>
<LI><FONT face=Garamond size=1>Blessed Hilt = Sheet Metal + Smithy Hammer + Ruby + Hilt Mold + Celestial Essence + Blessed Dust of Tunare + Mistletoe Temper (forge, <I>smithing trivial 181</I>) </FONT>
<LI><FONT face=Garamond size=1>Blessed Pommel = Sheet Metal + Smithy Hammer + Sapphire + Pommel Mold + Celestial Essence + Blessed Dust of Tunare + Mistletoe Temper (forge, <I>smithing trivial 182</I>) </FONT>
<LI><FONT face=Garamond size=1>Celestial Essence = 1 Celestial Solvent + 1 High End Research component (mortar and pestle, <I>no-fail combine</I>) </FONT>
<LI><FONT face=Garamond size=1>Mistletoe Temper = 1 Celestial Essence + 1 Elven Wine + 1 Mistletoe(brew barrel, <I>brewing trivial 136</I>) </FONT>
<LI><FONT face=Garamond size=1>Blessed Dust of Tunare = 1 Imbued Emerald + 1 Celestial Essence + 1 Jar of Acid (kiln, <I>pottery trivial 103</I>) </FONT></LI></UL>
<H4><FONT face=Garamond size=2>Third Gift of the Elves</FONT></H4>
<P><A href="http://www.eqtraders.com/items/show_item.php?item=1469&amp;menustr="><FONT face=Garamond color=#000000 size=1>Golden Idol Of Tunare</FONT></A><FONT face=Garamond size=1> </FONT></P>
<UL>
<LI><FONT face=Garamond size=1>Unfired Golden Idol of Tunare= 1 Gold Bar + 1 Idol Sketch + 1 enchanted block of clay + 1 water + 1 Celestial Essence + Sculpting Tools + 1 Vial of Distilled Mana + 1 Imbued Emerald (pottery wheel, <I>pottery trivial 242</I>) </FONT>
<LI><FONT face=Garamond size=1>Then combine Unfired Golden Idol of Tunare + Divine Crystalline Glaze + High Quality Firing Sheet (kiln, <I>firing trivial will be considerably lower than trivial on pottery wheel</I>) </FONT></LI></UL>
<P><FONT size=1><FONT face=Garamond><I>Other combines that you need</I> </FONT></FONT></P>
<UL>
<LI><FONT face=Garamond size=1>Celestial Essence = 1 Celestial Solvent + 1 High End Research component (mortar and pestle, <I>no-fail combine</I>) </FONT>
<LI><FONT face=Garamond size=1>Divine Crystalline Glaze = 1 Permafrost Crystals + 1 Iron Oxide + 1 White Lead + 1 water (glaze mortar, <I>no-fail combine</I>) </FONT>
<LI><FONT face=Garamond size=1>White Lead = Lead Sulfide + Limestone (mortar and pestle, <I>no-fail combine</I>) </FONT>
<LI><FONT face=Garamond size=1>enchanted block of clay is made by having an enchanter cast the level 8 Enchant Clay spell on a large block of clay </FONT></LI></UL><BR><BR><BR clear=all>
